<servcat id="35">
<name>SUSPENSION &amp; AXLE</name>
<section id="1002I_S000Z" variety="S000Z">
<name>SUSPENSION</name>
<ttl id="1002I_S000Z_72VBD_T005F" variety="T005F">
<name>REAR NO. 2 SUSPENSION ARM</name>
<para id="RM0000011E1004X" category="A" type-id="80001" name-id="SP0ZS-01" from="200601">
<name>REMOVAL</name>
<subpara id="RM0000011E1004X_01" type-id="01" category="01">
<s-1 id="RM0000011E1004X_01_0001">
<ptxt>REMOVE REAR WHEEL</ptxt>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM0000011E1004X_01_0003" proc-id="RM0250U___00003WV00000">
<ptxt>REMOVE REAR NO. 2 SUSPENSION ARM</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Remove the bolt, and disconnect the rear No. 2 suspension arm (inner side).</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C132489" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Remove the bolt, nut and the rear No. 2 suspension arm (outer side) from the rear axle carrier.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C132484" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<atten3>
<ptxt>When removing the bolt, keep the nut from rotating.</ptxt>
</atten3>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
</subpara>
</para>
</ttl>
</section>
</servcat>
</pub>
